    "_comment": "NOTE: Profile GUIDs below are well-known defaults generated by Windows Terminal. {61c54bbd-...} = Windows PowerShell 5, {0caa0dad-...} = cmd.exe, {b453ae62-...} = Azure Cloud Shell, {574e775e-...} = PowerShell 7 (from source: Windows.Terminal.PowershellCore). These are stable across standard installs but may differ if pwsh is installed to a non-default path or a preview build is used. If your PowerShell 7 GUID differs, update defaultProfile to match.",
